sql:
SELECT AVG(yards_gained) AS average_yards_gained
FROM plays
WHERE down = 1 AND yards_gained > 10;

external_knowledge:
- "sown the seeds of their legacy" metaphorically refers to making plays during the first quarter;
- "average harvest of yards" translates to the average yards gained per play;
- "total number of plays they've executed" represents the count of plays made by each quarterback.

sql:
SELECT SUM(yards_gained) AS total_yards
FROM plays
WHERE game_id = 123;
